import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
from datetime import datetime
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler
from sklearn.decomposition import FastICA
from sklearn.decomposition import PCA
from sklearn.manifold import TSNE
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

np.random.seed(42)

%load_ext autoreload
%autoreload 2

def df_standardScaler(X):
    scaler = StandardScaler()
    scaled_X = scaler.fit_transform(X)
    return pd.DataFrame(scaled_X, columns=X.columns)

def grafico_componenti(X, y, group_dict):
    for i,source in group_dict.items():
        plt.scatter(X[y == source, 0], X[y==source, 1], color=plt.cm.Set2(i),
                alpha=1, label=source)
    plt.legend()
    plt.xlabel("Prima componente")
    plt.ylabel("Seconda componente")
    plt.xticks([])
    plt.yticks([])

Definisco la matrice degli stem, il partito di appartenenza di ogni tweet e il dizionario dei partiti.

df = pd.read_csv('stem_matrix.csv', sep=',')
partiti, stem_matrix = df['vett_partito'], df[df.columns.difference(['vett_partito'])]

partiti_dict = {}
unique_partiti = list(set(partiti))
for i in range(len(unique_partiti)):
    partiti_dict[i+1] = unique_partiti[i]

Genero i grafici.

In [3]:
''' RAPPRESENTAZIONI GRAFICHE '''
print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] Start")
X_new = df_standardScaler(stem_matrix)

    
ica = FastICA(n_components=2, whiten=True)
X_ica2 = ica.fit_transform(X_new)
print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] ICA (2)")
plt.figure(figsize=(30, 20))
plt.title("ICA")
grafico_componenti(X_ica2, partiti, partiti_dict)
plt.show()


pca = PCA(n_components=2, whiten=True)
X_pca2 = pca.fit_transform(X_new)
print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] PCA (2)")
plt.figure(figsize=(30, 20))
plt.title("PCA")
grafico_componenti(X_pca2, partiti, partiti_dict)
plt.show()


X_tsne = TSNE(n_components=2).fit_transform(X_new)
print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] t-SNE")
plt.figure(figsize=(30, 20))
plt.title("t-SNE")
grafico_componenti(X_tsne, partiti, partiti_dict)
plt.show()


pca = PCA(n_components=X_new.shape[1], whiten=True)
X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X_new)
var = pca.explained_variance_ratio_
tot = [0]
for v in range(len(var)):
    tot += [ var[v]+tot[-1] ]
n_c = sum([j<0.80 for j in tot]) - 1
print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] PCA ("+str(X_new.shape[1])+")")
pca = PCA(n_components=n_c, whiten=True)
X_pca = pca.fit_transform(X_new)
print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] PCA ("+str(X_pca.shape[1])+")")
X_pca_tsne = TSNE(n_components=2).fit_transform(X_pca)
print('   ', round(sum(pca.explained_variance_ratio_),4), "=>", pca.explained_variance_ratio_[:5])
print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] PCA + t-SNE")
plt.figure(figsize=(30, 20))
plt.title("PCA + t-SNE")
grafico_componenti(X_pca_tsne, partiti, partiti_dict)
plt.show()   


print("["+datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")+"] End")
